The paper discusses a SPARQL engine for distributed RDF repositories, which involves data management and query processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DB (Databases), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
